data.meta_description: 189 likes, 3 comments - usambportugal on May 9, 2024: "Last night, Embassy Lisbon celebrated the relationship between Mário Soares and Frank Carlucci in honor of the Revolução dos Cravos. Thanks to our amazing panelists Marcia and Kristin Carlucci, João Soares and Fernanda Rollo who joined us at @FLAD_pt to discuss “A Path to Democracy”. Don’t forget to tune into our @USEmbPortugal YouTube channel to view the panel, and visit the Embassy’s website for the special exhibit we inaugurated at Casa Carlucci.".
